        <div class="msgSubject">My Gladiator review</div>
        <div class="sm notbold">
          
          Posted: 2010-10-25 22:38:12   | <input type="checkbox" name="quote-1288067892274561926" id="quote-1288067892274561926" class="msgQuoteCheck" onchange="multiQuote2()"/><label for="quote-1288067892274561926" onclick="multiQuote2()"> Quote</label>  | <a href="/forum.html?forum=175&amp;mid=1288067892274561926&amp;post=1&amp;replyto=1288067892274561926&amp;page=1" class="icon-replytothis" rel="nofollow">Reply to Post</a> | <a id="FOLLOW_MID_1288067892274561926" onclick="followToggle('add','1288067892274561926')" href="javascript:" class="icon-follow">Follow</a> 
